Class Club

  • java.lang.Object
    • Club

  • public class Club
extends java.lang.Object
    The Club class holds information about all climbers in the club including: The Climber within the Club who has recorded the highest average mountain height The highest Mountain recorded by a member of a Club A list of all Mountains that have been recorded, that are higher than a given level
    Version:
    1.0 (08/11/2017)
    Author:
    (Michael Westerby)
